latestIgtvVideos.title: 1 shirt, 11 ways (creative, yet simple)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Today I styled a staple piece that can be found in everyone's wardrobe.

People have been styling white shirts for ages now, so I did it as well but with my own variations. Even though some of these looks might be inspired, I've added my own twists to it. (feel free to dm me if you want to know how I created any of these looks)

Please like, share and comment if you enjoyed watching this 🧡

latestIgtvVideos.title: 1 Skirt, 6 Ways
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Fun fact : I bought this skirt at a flea market in Goa over 6 years ago and never wore it because it just looked and felt weird. I found this recently and decided to have some fun with it instead of throwing it out.

If you're as bored as I am, go look at your cupboard and maybe you'll find such a piece as well. Have fun with it and try styling it. I'd love for y'all to send me stuff y'all style.

And please like, share and comment if y'all enjoyed watching this video!
